REFERENCE	MANUAL_SAYINGS
LANG_ENGLISH	"SAYING COMMANDS\n\nThese commands are said out loud to execute them.\n\n- !ShowMOTD\nShow the Message of The Day\n\n- !HideMOTD\nHide the Message of The Day\n\n- !FreezeMOTD\nFreeze/UnFreeze the Message of The Day\n\n- !SlapMe\nGet slapped\n\n- !JetPack\nTake out or put away the jetpack\n\n- !EndDuel\nEnd a training duel"
LANG_CHINESE        "#same"

REFERENCE	MANUAL_ADMGUNS
LANG_ENGLISH	"ADMINISTRATION GUN CONTROLS\n\nThese can be bound to keys. Press the key while aiming at a client, and it will execute it on that client.\n\n- gun_freeze\nFreezes client solid, rendering them unable to move\n\n- gun_kick\nKick the client from the server\n\n- gun_silence\nStop a client from speaking\n\n- gun_insult\nCauses client to say whatever is defined in server.cfg\n\n- gun_terminator\nGive client all weapons and take away all force powers\n\n- gun_empower\nGive client all force powers, take away all weapons\n\n- gun_splat\nToss client into the air, and let them fall to their death\n\n- gun_slay\nKill a client\n\n- gun_monk\nTake away all force powers and weapons from a client\n\n- gun_sleep\nForce a client to sleep\n\n- gun_slap\nSmack a client into the air\n\n- gun_punish\nForce a client into the choke animation, and stop them from speaking"
LANG_CHINESE        "#same"

REFERENCE	MANUAL_CONFIGS
LANG_ENGLISH	"ONLINE SUPPORT\n\nYou can find support on the Clan Mod forums by the community at www.ClanMod.org/forums\n\nIf you are looking for BitValues for disabling emotes, custom administration levels, disabling certain commands, etc. look in the clanmod folder which is located in your GameData folder."
LANG_CHINESE        "#same"

REFERENCE	MANUAL_CMDS
LANG_ENGLISH	"COMMANDS\n\nThese commands can be entered into the console at any time.\n\n- JetPack\nPut on a jetpack\n\n- KnockMeDown\nKnock yourself down\n\n- DropSaber\nDrop your lightsaber\n\n- ShowMOTD\nShow the message of the day\n\n- FreezeMOTD\nFreeze the MOTD in place, type in again to unfreeze\n\n- HideMOTD\nHide the message of the day\n\n- EndDuel\nEnd a training duel\n\n- Who\nShow all clients, status, and client numbers\n\n- ChatColor\nChat in different colors\n\n- ToggleChat\nToggle teamchat mode\n\n- +button12\nShoot grappling hook\n\n- Ignore\nIgnore a client\n\n- ClanSay\nSpeak in clan mode\n\n- AdminSay\nSpeak in admin mode\n\n- Report\nReport something to an admin\n\n- SaberDamages\nView server's saber damages\n\n- WeaponDamages\nView server's weapon damages\n\n- Help\nView all Clan Mod commands\n- ServerTime\nView the server's time"
LANG_CHINESE        "#same"

REFERENCE	MANUAL_TITLE
LANG_ENGLISH	"Clan Mod Manual"
LANG_CHINESE        "#same"

REFERENCE	MANUAL_CREDITS
LANG_ENGLISH	"CREDITS\n\nSome code taken from these mods with permission\n- RealJedi\n- Duelers\n- TheLastHope\n- Open Jedi Project\n- XMod v2.0\n- Jedi Academy Empire v1.0\n\n\nSome code donated by\n- Razor Ace\n- cHoSen oNe\n- Bl b\n- Redsaurus\n- Ensiform\n- robo85045\n- Xharock\n\n\nSome tools developed by\n- Xanhorn\n- Alcore\n\n\nTranslations by\n- NECROM\n- Immunis\n- Stefan\n\n\nSpecial thanks to\n\nThe =NIO= clan, for beta testing, and supporting the project.\n\nLord_Darchind, for supporting my mod and finding bugs so I could fix them as soon as possible.\n\nRaptorServers.com for donating wonderful servers that I can use for testing purposes.\n\nAnd to the rest of the server hosters who helped support the mod by keeping their servers up.\n\n\nwww.ClanMod.org\nClan Mod is not associated with LucasArts in any way.\nAll material copyright of the respective coders and artists.\nUnauthorized redistribution is forbidden."
LANG_CHINESE        "#same"

REFERENCE	MANUAL_ADMCMDS
LANG_ENGLISH	"ADMINISTRATION COMMANDS\n\nSome admin commands can be toggled on or off by doing the command twice on a client.\n\n- amBan\nBan a client from the server\n\n- DemiGod\nTurn a client into a demigod (noclip)\n\n- GrantAdmin\nGrant administration to a client\n\n- Protect\nProtect a client from receiving damage\n\n- Terminator\nGive a client all weapons and inifinte ammo\n\n- Slay\nKill a client\n\n- Rename\nChange a clients name\n\n- Silence\nStop a client from talking\n\n- InsultSilence\nMake a client say whats defined in server.cfg\n\n- Splat\nThrow a client in the air and let him fall to his death\n\n- Empower\nGive a client all force powers\n\n- Freeze\nFreeze a client in place\n\n- NPC\nSpawn an NPC\n\n- Scale\nScale a client to a certain height\n\n- ChangeMap\nChange the server's gametype and map\n\n- AdminTele\nTeleport a client to a certain position, or to another client\n\n- amKick\nKick a client from the server\n\n- AdminBan\nBan someone from administration\n\n- LockName\nMake a client unable to change their name\n\n- CSPrint\nPrint a message on the center of the screen\n\n- ForceTeam\nForce a client to a certain team\n\n- Monk\nTake away all force powers and weapons from a client\n\n- Sleep\nMake a client fall asleep\n\n- Punish\nLock a client into the choke animation, and make them unable to speak\n\n- Slap\nSmack a client into the air\n\n- LockTeam\nMake a team unable to join\n\n- AddModel\nAdd a model to the map, on your position\n\n- AddEffect\nAdd an effect to the map, on your position\n\n- MyAdminCommands\nShow your admin level's specific allowed admin commands\n\n- ChangeMode\nChange the mode of the gametype\n\n- AdminCP\nOpen the administration control panel\n\n- WhoIP\nDisplays client's IP addresses\n- AmVSTR\nExecute the vstr.cfg file, and vstr a variable from it"
LANG_CHINESE        "#same"

